videos.description: Greg McCrae finds a gap and runs 11 yards into the end zone for a UCF touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF scores early with 11-yd TD

videos.description: Taj McGowan picks up his 6th rushing touchdown of the season with a 2-yard dive, giving the Knights a 14-0 lead over the Midshipmen.
videos.headline: McGowan gives UCF comfortable lead

videos.description: McKenzie Milton connects with Dredrick Snelson for a 34-yard UCF touchdown.
videos.headline: Milton finds Snelson for 34-yd TD

videos.description: Zach Abey squeezes into the end zone for a 5-yard Navy touchdown.
videos.headline: Navy closes gap with 5-yd TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton runs for a 1-yard Knights touchdown, increasing their lead to 28-10.
videos.headline: UCF TD parade rolls on with Milton keeper

videos.description: Mike Martin weaves through defenders for a 14-yard Midshipmen touchdown.
videos.headline: Navy answers with 14-yd TD

videos.description: Navy's Zach Abey finds an opening and runs in for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Abey keeps Navy in game with TD run
